---
title: sidecar_retention (fulu-validator)
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB

    [*] --> q_init : start
    q_init --> q_check : current_epoch - sidecar_epoch <= MIN_EPOCHS_FOR_DATA_COLUMN_SIDECARS_REQUESTS
    q_check --> q_hold : within retention period
    q_check --> q_prune_check : retention period expired
    q_hold --> q_serve : serve sidecar on request
    q_serve --> [*] : done
    q_prune_check --> q_prune : MAY prune sidecars
    q_prune --> [*] : done

    note right of q_check
        INV: Sidecars MUST be retained for MIN_EPOCHS_FOR_DATA_COLUMN_SIDECARS_REQUESTS epochs
        INV: Sidecars MUST be served when requested during retention period
        INV: Pruning is optional (MAY) only after retention period expires
    end note
